## Temporary/backup files (general)

*~
*.bak
*.tmp
*.old
*.swp
*.swo
*.swn
*.asd
*.orig

## Word/Excel temp files
# (patterns must not carry trailing comments — Git treats the whole
# line as the pattern)

~$*
# Word backup
*.wbk
# Excel backup
*.xlk
# File lock indicators
*.lock

## Build artifacts

build.log
output.pdf

## Affinity autosave/backup (safe to ignore)

*.autosave
*.afdesign-preview
*.afphoto-preview
*.afpub-preview

## Template files
# These lines are commented out by default, meaning the template files
# (.tex, .lua, .yaml, .sh) ARE tracked by Git.
#
# If you want to keep the template files OUT of your content repo (e.g.,
# you installed them globally or share them across projects), uncomment
# the lines below:

